@startuml sd_SocialSecurityService_calculate
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title SocialSecurityService.calculate(employee, yearMonth) - 社保公积金计算

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryCalculationService" as CalcSvc
participant "SocialSecurityService" as SSvc
participant "SocialSecurityConfigRepository" as CfgRepo
participant "SocialSecurityConfig\n(实体)" as Cfg

Client -> CalcSvc: calculateAll(yearMonth, trialRun, username)
CalcSvc -> SSvc: calculate(employee, yearMonth)
SSvc -> SSvc: 提取year=2024, city="北京"
SSvc -> CfgRepo: findByCityAndYearAndActiveTrue("北京", 2024)
alt 无城市配置
  CfgRepo --> SSvc: empty
  SSvc -> CfgRepo: findByYearAndActiveTrue(2024)
  alt 仍无配置
    SSvc -> SSvc: getDefaultConfigs()\n默认费率
  end
end
alt 有配置
  CfgRepo --> SSvc: List<SocialSecurityConfig>
end
note right of SSvc #F0F8FF
  **逐险种计算(循环):**
  养老: base × 8%
  医疗: base × 2%
  失业: base × 0.5%
  工伤: 个人0%
  生育: 个人0%
  公积金: base × 7%
  ---------------------------------
  base = clamp(基数, 下限, 上限)
  社保合计 = 养老+医疗+失业(+工伤+生育)
  公积金合计 = base × 公积金比例
end note
SSvc --> CalcSvc: Map<String, Double>\n{ "socialInsurance": 880.00,\n  "housingFund": 700.00 }
CalcSvc --> Client: 存入SalaryRecord
@enduml
